@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.43 + 0.09)
    v0 = 0.38
    tmp = ((0.60 + (v0 + 0.82 / tmp + 0.11)) + tmp)
    v2 = (0.30 + 0.31)

    v2 = (0.39 * wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.67)))
